propsSchema.description:
Code editor with multi-language syntax highlighting. Syncs content with a canvas parameter.

## Example — SQL

```json
{
  "type": "code-editor",
  "props": {
    "param": "my_query",
    "language": "sql",
    "defaultValue": "SELECT * FROM {{my_udf}} LIMIT 10"
  }
}
```

## Example — Python

```json
{
  "type": "code-editor",
  "props": {
    "param": "code",
    "language": "python",
    "defaultValue": "import pandas as pd"
  }
}
```
